{"tid":778752,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解咁難肥","createTime":"2018-08-14T02:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T02:39:20.000Z","uid":193722,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b27a4bfce2c817a11b68f59102298e3a0cbeac93","tid":778752,"uid":193722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T02:28:45.000Z","msg":"平時正常3餐飲食，間唔中食下宵夜，本人亦都係屬於為食類型，食量都唔錯。<br />\n間唔中都會出街食好西，同班fd 打邊勞 / 放題  永遠都可以食到最後先投降。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每星期都有運動 踢下波同跑下步咁。<br />\n<br />\n但你老母，咁多年黎都冇肥過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。 一黎太瘦踢波冇身位 好易俾人搶到波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n二黎肥d著3出街都好睇d麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我知食極唔肥會得罪好多人，但真心想增磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 2X男 身高168cm 重54kg"},{"pid":"8aae79d67ab06fb34c204f92a49cae86a7a4aeae","tid":778752,"uid":78139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T02:30:33.000Z","msg":"加油巴打<br />\n好多時候要肥都好睇心理壓力 想肥都唔可以急 生活都盡量開心d 會易d增重既<br />\n利申 173 60kg 同樣增緊肥 共勉之"},{"pid":"3e7c7ef4dcf44d02d360dd4db63eb4fdb79c7b9b","tid":778752,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T02:31:19.000Z","msg":"腸胃好唔好<br />\n似係吸收問題多"},{"pid":"7e1c97ba715d0a47d91884ecb900f293bd5861a1","tid":778752,"uid":193722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e7c7ef4dcf44d02d360dd4db63eb4fdb79c7b9b","tid":778752,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T02:31:19.000Z","msg":"腸胃好唔好<br />\n似係吸收問題多"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T02:32:44.000Z","msg":"點先知自己腸胃好唔好。 我差唔多每日/格日 就有屎柯"},{"pid":"1b50aa6aca9856613e68555147af4a6cf520b0ad","tid":778752,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e1c97ba715d0a47d91884ecb900f293